ng explained about his stage name saying, \"the name means the lowest level of Buddhist hell\". He said he added an extra 'i' since someone else was using that name on MySpace.\nAfter Bergling's death, pop singer Madonna tweeted, \"So Sad... So Tragic. Good Bye Dear Sweet Tim. \ud83d\udc99 Gone too Soon.\""}
