se government to extradite people accused of crimes from Hong Kong and try them under the mainland's legal system. The protests have since transitioned to focus on other issues associated with Chinese encroachment on Hong Konger's rights, such as the way the Hong Kong legislature is elected, and on the actions of police toward protesters."}
